title: Raven-Symone apologizes; dad rebukes her - Click Orlando
text:
"The View" co-host's father also didn't dig her comments Thursday on the daytime talk show, on which she said she would discriminate against job applicants with a "ghetto name." In a Facebook post, Christopher B. Pearman responded to what he said was one woman's comment that she would not buy his book about raising a child star because of what his daughter said.
